ingredients: FILTERED WATER, CASEIN* (MILK PROTEIN), CANOLA OIL, MODIFIED POTATO STARCH, SALT, RICE FLOUR, TAPIOCA STARCH, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, POTATO STARCH AND POWDERED CELLULOSE ADDED TO PREVENT CAKING, NATURAL FLAVOR, LACTIC ACID (NON-DAIRY), SODIUM CITRATE, CALCIUM PHOSPHATE, MONO AND DIGLYCERIDES, SORBIC ACID (PRESERVATIVE), CARRAGEENAN, ISOLATED SOY PROTEIN, NATAMYCIN (A NATURAL MOLD INHIBITOR), ENZYMES, VITAMINS AND MINERALS. VITAMINS AND MINERALS: VITAMIN E, VITAMIN A PALMITATE, VITAMIN C, FERRIC ORTHOPHOSPHATE, VITAMIN B12, VITAMIN D3, FOLIC ACID, VITAMIN B6, RIBOFLAVIN (VITAMIN B2).
